title: Channel24.co.za | Jeannie D reveals her biggest fear!
text:
Jeannie D reveals her biggest fear! 2015-10-22 10:17 
Johannesburg – In the spirit of Halloween Sony Max (DStv 128) offers some of the best Halloween entertainment that will both terrify and delight you. 
The reality series in which contestants face their biggest fear, Fear Factor will be airing on the channel Monday to Friday at 20:00 
Hosted by Joe Rogan contestants must decide if they have the guts and determination to face their fears while outpacing the competition. 
Here are two local celebs who dished on their biggest fears: 
Television presenter Jeannie D's biggest fear is of the automobile kind. 
"My biggest fear is having a car accident which is why I did an advanced driving course, just to make sure I am in control and can hopefully do my best to avoid an accident,” says Jeannie D. 
Prime Circle frontman Neil Breytenbach on the other hand has a cold blooded fear. 
“Snakes, snakes, snakes. They freak me out and I don’t understand them... they just freak-me-out!”, says Neil. 
Catch Fear Factor season 1 and 2, Monday - Friday at 20:00 on Sony Max (DStv 128)! 
(Photos supplied)
